Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:23.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共感も栄光も賞賛も欲しがるのは野暮ってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:26.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}正体不明の引力が常識を無に帰す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:28.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}引き金を引いてしまうから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:33.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}冗談じゃねえよ Phantom's begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:35.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}嘘にまみれきって蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}心まで霞んで蜃気楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善々悪々も審議不能になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:45.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全部嫌になった　それさえも幸せな結末だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だめだ　そんな悲しいこと言うな　まだ世界は生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:52.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}君が泣いてたって生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}だからこの空の先を見たい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}邪魔すぎる運命のターゲット睨みながら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:04.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}言えそうで良かった「まだ愛していたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:56.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}為錯位的焦點所惑 四下尋找說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,0:00:59.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}看吧枯葉起舞 終會化為蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}然後調節到位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:02.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,0)\blur2\be1}然後是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:06.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}時過境遷太急 秒速開始不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:08.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全因自己武斷的選擇開端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以必須做出了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:14.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}無聊的理由 是停止思考的鐵證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}無法守護應守護之物 那就不要亂出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:23.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}共鳴 榮光 稱讚 都不應奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:26.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不明真相的引力 將常識歸於虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.91,0:01:28.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}會扣下扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:33.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不是開玩笑的 幻覺已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:35.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,500)\blur2\be1}充滿謊言的海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}讓心都變得模糊的海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}善善惡惡都無法評議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:45.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}全都變得討厭 連這都是幸福的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}不行 不要說得如此悲涼 世界依然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:52.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}即使你會哭泣也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}所以想看到這片天空的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:00.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,200)\blur2\be1}一邊瞪視過於礙眼的命運的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:04.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fax0\fscx100\t(700,1000,\fax0.3\fscx90)\fad(0,800)\blur2\be1}能說出口就好 “還想繼續愛”
